query:
WITH ranked AS (
                                SELECT user_id,
                                       ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY position) AS new_pos
                                FROM krapbott_v2.queue
                                WHERE channel_id = $1
                            )
                            UPDATE krapbott_v2.queue q
                            SET position = r.new_pos
                            FROM ranked r
                            WHERE q.user_id = r.user_id
                              AND q.channel_id = $1
